Package: MCC
Title: Functions for Comparing Mean Cumulative Count Curves
Version: 0.5.4
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Zachary",
           family = "McCaw",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "zmccaw@alumni.harvard.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2006-9828"))
Description: Provides functions for estimating the mean cumulative count curve, using the method of Ghosh and Lin (2000) <doi:10.1111/j.0006-341X.2000.00554.x>, and for comparing two treatment arms with respect to the difference and ratio in areas under the mean cumulative count curve.
